itemLabel: Princess Helena of Waldeck and Pyrmont
itemDescription: (1861-1922); wife of Prince Leopold, Duke of Albany; daughter of George Victor, Prince of Waldeck and Pyrmont

wikipedia_page.main: Princess Helen of Waldeck and Pyrmont (later Duchess of Albany; 17 February 1861 – 1 September 1922) was a member of the British royal family by marriage. She was the fifth daughter and child of George Victor, Prince of Waldeck and Pyrmont, and his first wife, Princess Helena of Nassau.
